Package: brat
Type: Package
Title: HTML widget, shiny gadget and shiny app to expose the visualization and annotation 
  functionality of the brat rapid annotation tool for pure R annotation workflows
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2021-03-25
Authors@R: person("Andreas", "Blaette", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "andreas.blaette@uni-due.de")
Description: This package exposes the visualization and annotation functionality of the 'brat'
  rapid annotation tool (<https://brat.nlplab.org/>). The purpose is facilitate implementing advanced 
  pure R annotation  workflows in a lightweight manner. Based on an HTML widget 'brat', a HTML gadget
  ('bradget') and a shiny app ('brainy') are tools offered for annotating entities and relations in
  single or multiple documents. The  JavaScript code of 'brat' and the JavaScript libraries 'jQuery',
  'jQuery SVG' and 'sprintf' are MIT-licensed. The license of the R package is GPL-3.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    methods
